scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 363-497 contain the full text of the Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the negotiated terms between the parties. The lines before 363 are the standard pre-printed Master Agreement, and lines after 497 are signatures and page numbers. This span excludes the standard form and any annexes, focusing solely on the Schedule.
